org.bff.javampd.album

Class MPDAlbumDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bff.javampd.album.MPDAlbumDatabase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AlbumDatabase

    public class MPDAlbumDatabase
extends Object
implements AlbumDatabase
    MPDAlbumDatabase represents a album database to a MPD. To obtain an instance of the class you must use the MusicDatabase.getAlbumDatabase() method from the MPD connection class.
    Author:
    Bill
